name: Voodoo Automaton
description: The voodoo automatons were born of the pain and suffering of the age of steam. Crafted by SalaCorp workers from scraps of stone, blood stained rags and stuffed with the hair of those poisoned by fumes from the mine, these voodoo dolls took on a life of their own, skin hardening to stone as they consumed the souls of dying SalaCorp workers. They now wander the earth stalking Corp executives, watching and waiting for the perfect time to strike. This is my 2nd NFT in the steampunk collection.
